body:





- - Web Component
    - Custom HTML elements
    - Shadow DOM
    - Templates & Slots
    - HTML Imports (discontinued)
    - ![image-20200517110913499](/home/guido/Downloads/image-20200517110913499.png)
  - Why web components?
    - Encapsulate Logic + UI
      - Easy to understand
      - Easy to maintain
      - Separation of Concerns
    - Re-usable across page
      - Use it like a normal HTML element
      - Don't worry about overlapping logic
      - Write logic + UI only once
    - Re-usable between projects
      - We can use it on different frameworks (sharing the same web component from a Angular project to a React project)
      - Re-use core UI elements across projects
      - DRY logic and UI code
      - The web components can be published as a package (npm) 
